  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we focus on two different quantitative performance measures: keyword overlap and sentence similarity.",
    "For the former, we use a comprehensive glossary of human-curated dermatological vocabularies 31 to extract important medical keywords from the ground truth notes.",
    "In addition, we use ScispaCy 32, a biomedical named entity recognition (NER) tool, to capture a broader range of technical terms.",
    "We then determine how many keywords from the ground truth text can be found in the generated text.",
    "The Jaccard index is used to quantify their overlap."
  ],
